==== Second-round transfers

{reference} https://justinlall.wordpress.com/2005/06/20/transfer-extensions/[
_Transfer Extensions_]
__ {nbsp}{ndash}{nbsp} Justin Lall

Second-round transfers apply after a Jacoby transfer to a major.
They are descriptive, not demanding.

Transfer to {H} then 2S (_transfer to 2NT_{thinsp}) does not
show spades.
It is invitational with exactly five hearts and fewer than
four spades.
Opener assumes that it is one of: +
@ balanced or semi-balanced inv. +
