==== With four-card support

Our super-accept scheme is ON, except that opener may use a reverse
transfer to make responder declare.

Anti-splinter super-accepts (showing values, four-card-support and
minumum) neither confirm nor deny control.
A subsequent 3NT by responder shows control of the transfer-suit and
is a slam try with preference to declare.

